headline.main: Mississippi Statues at US Capitol Up for Discussion
headline.print_headline: Mississippi Statues at US Capitol Up for Discussion

lead_paragraph: Mississippi Gov. Phil Bryant says he'd be willing to talk about possibly replacing the statues that represent the state in the U.S. Capitol in Washington.
